                TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts19" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts21">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>gālūč bī-ya haḏāk al-ḥašīš bī-ya al tara činne baʕdan nuḏ̣rub-u qazme aṣ-ṣubuḥ uxṛa ṭālʕa. </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
