                TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts39" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts40">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>šilt īd-i lē fōg b-al-ḥabis, gilit, yā rabb-i inta karīm inta raḥīm inta ǧaʕad ᵊššūf-ni āni mā-li sūč yāw! </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
