                TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts57" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts59">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>āni agūl čibīr ʕid-na ʕammo ʕumr-u xamsa w ṯalāṯīn, w-al-nahār min nahārāt šift-u gām yitiḥakkar ʕalay-ye. </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
