                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>w-inta lē-k ʕiǧyān ḥurumt-ak baṛṛa, uṭluʕ baṛṛa yā ṣābūr yā aḷḷa nōba sāwēt sūč. </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
